#: ../../source/api/trade.rst:19
msgid "Balance engine"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:1 of
msgid "Supply balance engine (v0.4 #12)．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:3 of
msgid "島単位で「生産 / 消費 / delta」の per-product バランスを算出する．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:5 of
msgid "## 依存"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:7 of
msgid "``FactoryAggregate`` (trade.factories) — 供給側 (factory instance 群)"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:8 of
msgid ""
"``FactoryRecipeTable`` (trade.factory_recipes) — Calculator 由来の tpmin / "
"outputs マップ"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:10 of
msgid "``ResidenceAggregate.tier_breakdown`` (trade.population) — tier 別の人口"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:11 of
msgid "``ConsumptionTable`` (trade.consumption) — tier × product の tpmin/人"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:13 of
msgid "## 計算式"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:15 of
msgid ""
"**生産量 (ton/min)** = Σ over factory instances of ``productivity × "
"recipe.tpmin × output.amount``"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:17 of
msgid ""
"**消費量 (ton/min)** = Σ over tier × needs of ``tier.resident_total × "
"need.tpmin`` - ``is_bonus_need`` の物資は通常消費に含めない - **unlock "
"未達の物資は除外**．Calculator の ``tier.needs`` は tier の"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:21 of
msgid ""
"潜在的な全 need 候補．書記長の島で実際 unlock されてるかは "
"``ResidenceAggregate.product_saturations`` (save の ``ConsumptionStates`` "
"観測値) で判定し，観測されてない need は加算しない (「ビスケット 要求されてないのに消費加算される」問題の修正)．observe "
"ゼロの島は tier.needs を素直に使う (都市再建直後など tier breakdown だけで推定 したいフォールバック)．"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:27 of
msgid "**delta** = produced - consumed"
msgstr ""

#: anno_save_analyzer.trade.balance:29 of
msgid "複数島の集計は ``SupplyBalanceTable.aggregate`` で area_manager 集合を指定 して行う．"
msgstr ""

